00:00:18.330 --> 00:00:19.130 align:middle line:90%
>>GEORGE NOORY: Hi.

00:00:19.130 --> 00:00:21.540 align:middle line:10%
I'm George Noory and welcome
back to "Beyond Belief."

00:00:21.540 --> 00:00:25.020 align:middle line:10%
