today is a dramatic program

00:00:25.020 --> 00:00:27.580 align:middle line:10%
that has to do with
the Federal Reserve.

00:00:27.580 --> 00:00:30.320 align:middle line:84%
So many people believe
the Federal Reserve

00:00:30.320 --> 00:00:32.380 align:middle line:90%
is part of the US government.

00:00:32.380 --> 00:00:37.917 align:middle line:84%
As you will hear from G.
Edward Griffin, it is not.

00:00:37.917 --> 00:00:40.250 align:middle line:84%
>>ANNOUNCER: He has challenged
the status quo and pushed

00:00:40.250 --> 00:00:42.000 align:middle line:90%
