book, The Creature

00:00:46.480 --> 00:00:50.530 align:middle line:10%
from Jekyll Island, which
exposes the Federal Reserve.

00:00:50.530 --> 00:00:54.480 align:middle line:84%
Since the 1960s, Griffin
has confronted conspiracies

00:00:54.480 --> 00:00:57.790 align:middle line:84%
