there going crazy

00:35:56.240 --> 00:35:59.540 align:middle line:84%
because that's more money
than he's ever had this life.

00:35:59.540 --> 00:36:04.540 align:middle line:84%
The guy goes to his safe
and brings back a tray full

00:36:04.540 --> 00:36:10.890 align:middle line:84%
of $500,000, gives it to Saul,
and Saul is just like in shock.

00:36:10.890 --> 00:36:13.390 align:middle line:84%
But he starts
looking at the money

00:36:13.390 --> 00:36:17.640 align:middle line:84%
and it's printed up with
that guy's face on it.

00:36:17.640 --> 00:36:20.470 align:middle line:84%
