00:36:31.550 --> 00:36:35.840 align:middle line:84%
And the guy said, in due time
it'll be worth something.

00:36:35.840 --> 00:36:38.707 align:middle line:84%
I kind of feel that way
about our money right now.

00:36:38.707 --> 00:36:41.290 align:middle line:84%
>>GRIFFIN: Well, which way, that
it's going down or coming up?

00:36:41.290 --> 00:36:42.120 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That it's going down.

00:36:42.120 --> 00:36:42.590 align:middle line:90%
>>GRIFFIN: Going down.

00:36:42.590 --> 00:36:43.470 align:middle line:90%
Well, yes.

00:36:43.470 --> 00:36:45.600 align:middle line:84%
