purchasing power of it.

00:36:45.600 --> 00:36:48.140 align:middle line:84%
You don't have to go
any further than that.

00:36:48.140 --> 00:36:52.870 align:middle line:84%
When the Federal Reserve bills
were introduced back in 1913,

00:36:52.870 --> 00:36:54.860 align:middle line:84%
they had the
